### Get all states
GET https://lexi-dcdrc-api.onrender.com/states

### Get commissions for a state (replace STATE_ID)
GET https://lexi-dcdrc-api.onrender.com/commissions/1

### Search cases by case number
POST https://lexi-dcdrc-api.onrender.com/cases/by-case-number
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "state": "KARNATAKA",
  "commission": "Bangalore 1st & Rural Additional",
  "search_value": "123/2025"
}

